prodNameC: "銳盟" 威克菌流行性嗜血桿菌b型檢測套組(未滅菌)
ingredientsDesc:
Test Latex
0.5% suspension of polystyrene latex particles in glycine-buffered saline pH 8.2 containing 0.1% sodium azide as preservative. The latex particles are coated with rabbit antibody to H. influenzae type b antigen.
Control Latex
0.5% suspension of polystyrene latex particles in glycine-buffered saline pH 8.2 containing 0.1% sodium azide as preservative. The latex particles are coated with non-immune rabbit globulins.
Polyvalent Positive Control
antigen from a representative strain of H. influenzae type b.
Negative Control
Glycine saline buffer, pH 8.2. Contains 0.05% Bronidox® as preservative.
